  \begin {tikzcd}
    Fx\ar [r, "Fh"]\ar [d, "f"'] & Fy\ar [d, "g"]\\
    x\ar [r, "h"'] & y
  \end {tikzcd}


 commutes.

The Eilenberg-Moore category C^T is terminal in the
category of resolutions of a monad. Explicitly, for a
resolution 





